Golze Group's Wiki
==================

Welcome to the source code of the Wiki of the Golze Group. These project uses [Sphinx](https://www.sphinx-doc.org/en/master/) to authomatically generate the documentation. As such, new content is added in the [reStructuredText](https://www.sphinx-doc.org/en/master/usage/restructuredtext/basics.html) markup language.

## Quick startup

Create the new documentation files (*e.g.* newdoc.rst) inside the **source** directory. Then modify the file **source/index.rst** to add the new documentation file without the extension:

```
.. toctree::
    :maxdepth: 2
    :caption: Contents
    :titlesonly:

    fhi_aims
    general_tud
    newdoc
```
